<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4632023>
    dc:description "Figure 1. Colobomatus collettei Cressey, 1977, adult female. (A) Habitus, ventral; (B) antennule, ventral; (C) buccal capsule and mouthparts, ventral; (D) leg 1, ventrolateral; (E) leg 2, ventrolateral; (F) leg 3, ventrolateral; (G) posterior end of abdomen and caudal rami, ventral. Abbreviations: A, antenna; la, labium; mx, maxillule; Mx, maxilla." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4632023/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

